Find all integers 
\begin_inset Formula $k\in\left[1,10\right]$
\end_inset

 such that there are at least three different integers 
\begin_inset Formula $j$
\end_inset

, where 
\begin_inset Formula $1\leq j\leq k$
\end_inset

, each 
\begin_inset Formula $j$
\end_inset

 satisfying the condition 
\begin_inset Formula $j*j>2*k$
\end_inset

.
